								<a href="#p39168">Re: Secure file deletion</a>
			</h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="./viewtopic.php?p=39168&amp;sid=113b3da9121bde1fbb11e29757440691#p39168"><img src="./styles/Carbon/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>			by <strong><a href="./memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=14322&amp;sid=113b3da9121bde1fbb11e29757440691">Goatboy</a></strong> on Thu May 27, 2010 2:40 pm			<br />([msg=39168]see Re: Secure file deletion[/msg])
